quran[11{c,v,t}:
18,35,aur ( aisi shakhiyon ) se apne haq mein zulm karta howa apne baagh mein daakhil howa. kehnay laga ke mein nahi khayaal karta ke yeh baagh kabhi tabah ho
18,36,aur nah khayaal karta hon ke qayamat barpaa ho. aur agar mein apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lotaya bhi jaoon to ( wahan ) zaroor is se achi jagah paon ga
18,37,to is ka dost jo is se guftagu kar raha tha kehnay laga kekiya tum is ( khuda ) se kufar karte ho jis ne tum ko matti se pedakiya phir nutfay se phir tumhe poora mard banaya
18,38,magar mein to yeh kehta hon ke khuda hi mera perwar-digaar hai aur mein apne perwar-digaar ke sath kisi ko shareek nahi karta
18,39,aur ( bhala ) jab tum apne baagh mein daakhil hue to tum ne mashah allah quwwata illalbillah kyun nah kaha. agar tum mujhe maal o aulaad mein apne se kamtar dekhte ho
18,40,to ajab nahi ke mera perwar-digaar mujhe tumahray baagh se behtar ataa farmaiye aur is ( tumahray baagh ) par aasman se aafat bhaij day to woh saaf maidan hojaye
18,41,ya is ( ki neher ) ka pani gehra hojaye to phir tum usay nah laa sako
18,42,aur is ke mewoon ko azaab ne aa ghera aur woh apni chatriyon par gir kar reh gaya. to jo maal is ne is par kharchkiya tha is par ( hasrat se ) haath milnay laga aur kehnay laga ke kash mein apne perwar-digaar ke sath kisi ko shareek nah banata
18,43,( is waqt ) khuda ke siwa koi jamaat is ki madadgaar nah hui aur nah woh badla le saka
18,44,yahan ( se saabit howa ke ) hukoomat sab khuday-e brhq hi ki hai. isi ka sila behtar aur ( isi ka ) badla acha hai
18,45,aur un se duniya ki zindagi ki misaal bhi bayan kardo ( woh aisi hai ) jaisay pani jisay hum ne aasman se barsaya. to is ke sath zameen ki roedgi mil gayi. phir woh choora choora hogayi ke hawae usay urati phurti hain. aur khuda to har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
